<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1241967-one-of-my-teachers-said-that-this-book-was">One of my teachers said that this book was controversial because it seemed to target Islam more than other religions. If you read the book, what are your thoughts about this? Is it true in your opinion? *I haven&#39;t read the book myself and don&#39;t know if I will yet.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1241967'><a id="like_count_community_question_1241967" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1241967?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">4 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F43369.God_Is_Not_Great">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1241967-one-of-my-teachers-said-that-this-book-was">4 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1241967-one-of-my-teachers-said-that-this-book-was">See all 7 answers</a>
</li>
