      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/3442838-god-is-not-great-how-religion-poisons-everything">Quotes from God Is Not Great:...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Human decency is not derived from religion. It precedes it.&rdquo;</span>
